<div class='installation'>
<h3>Installation</h3>
<p>
At the command prompt, in the root of your Radiant project, type:
</p>
<pre><code>script/extension install sns_page_hook</code></pre>
<p>You can install it as a gem too. <code>gem install radiant-sns_page_hook-extension</code></p>
